    "description": "<strong>Rhythm Stones is a 1 button 3D rhythm game that crosses moving stepping stones.</strong><br><br><br><strong>1. Cross the 3D stepping stones to the beat!</strong><br><br>Rhythm Stones is a 3D rhythm game in which you cross the moving stepping stones to the beat. The stepping stones move in various types of 3D space; flat, cylindrical, spherical, and random!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/fe1bc17b5a9b915e6bfad9b55c2337d9.poster.avif?t=1729048501\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/fe1bc17b5a9b915e6bfad9b55c2337d9.webm?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/fe1bc17b5a9b915e6bfad9b55c2337d9.mp4?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>2. Simple controls, but hardcore difficulty!</strong><br><br>Rhythm Stones lets you press any key to play, but can you get past all of the difficult beats until the end?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/9474782cd9b94949ed54c0e85d59f5ad.poster.avif?t=1729048501\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/9474782cd9b94949ed54c0e85d59f5ad.webm?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/9474782cd9b94949ed54c0e85d59f5ad.mp4?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>3. But even if you fail, special items allow you to succeed over time!</strong><br><br>The more you lose a level, the more health-increasing items appear. No matter how difficult the stage is, if you keep trying you will surely succeed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/89f828844e383db638dc37ade1b9c964.poster.avif?t=1729048501\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/89f828844e383db638dc37ade1b9c964.webm?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/89f828844e383db638dc37ade1b9c964.mp4?t=1729048501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>4. Enjoy 56 songs in various genres!</strong><br><br>Rhythm Stones consists of 56 stages (including 5 tutorials), and each stage consists of a different song in various genres such as rock, funk, jazz, EDM, acoustic, etc.<br><br><br><strong>※ Game Tip</strong> <br><br>Rhythm monsters help you know the next beat, so it's very important to memorize each rhythm monster's pattern. In particular, the black rhythm monster (8th note) and the green rhythm monster (quarter note) appear the most!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175450/extras/1a766e057db44e5d544723ef572f811c.avif?t=1729048501\" width=576 height=324 /></span>",
